<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ف ل ذ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٨٢٩ - ف ل ذ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فلَّذَ يُفَلِّذ، تفليذًا، فهو مُفَلِّذ، والمفعول مُفَلَّذ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• فلَّذَ الشَّيءَ:</span> قطَّعه <span class="c1">"فلَّذ اللَّحْمَ كما أراد المشتري"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>